text: Homogenic is an album by Björk. It was released in 1997. Music critic Sal Cinquemani said that it is the best electronic music album of the 1990s. Pitchfork gave it 9.9 out of 10.https://www.webcitation.org/5g3suOZf7 Five singles were released from the album.
